<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-15058] Avoid double counting read latencies for digest queries</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-15058</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We are closing the &lt;tt&gt;UnfilteredPartitionIterator&lt;/tt&gt; wrapped with &lt;tt&gt;withMetricsRecording&lt;/tt&gt; twice when we get digest requests - closing it calls &lt;tt&gt;onClose&lt;/tt&gt; and that makes the metrics update twice.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
